verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Complete, complete, complete in Him,
We are complete in Him.
Complete, complete, complete in Him,
We are complete in Him.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
It's not by works of righteousness
But by His grace alone.
It's not by works of righteousness
But by His grace alone.
It's not by works of righteousness
But by His grace alone.
We are complete in Him.

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
There's nothing more that I can do
'Cause Jesus did it all.
There's nothing more that I can do
'Cause Jesus did it all.
There's nothing more that I can do
'Cause Jesus did it all.
We are complete in Him.

verse.name: v4
verse.lines:
The fullness of the Godhead bodily
Dwelleth in the Lord.
The fullness of the Godhead bodily
Dwelleth in the Lord.
The fullness of the Godhead bodily
Dwelleth in the Lord.
We are complete in Him.
